 1994-19511994-11-250,  ,  ,  EA,  , 
PrecisAppointment of Simon Wade as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Suriname; James Fox as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of El Salvador; Art Wright as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Botswana with concurrent accreditation as Ambassador of Canada to the People's Republic of Angola as well as to the Republic of Mozambique; Réjean Frenette as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Bénin; Marc Brault as High Commissioner for Canada to the Kingdom of Lesotho as well as High Commissioner for Canada to the Kingdom of Swaziland; Peter Sutherland as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Yemen; Russel Davidson as Ambassador of Canada to the Dominican Republic; Arsène A. Després as Ambassador of Canada to the Central African Republic; Lucie Geneviève Edwards as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Uganda with concurrent accreditation as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Rwanda as well as to the Republic of Burundi; J. Christopher Poole as Ambassador of Canada to the Sultanate of Oman concurrently accredited as Ambassador of Canada to the State of Qatar; Jeremy K.B. Kinsman as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Armenia with concurrent accreditation as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Tadjikistan, the Republic of Kazakhstan, the Republic of Uzbekistan, the Republic of Belarus, the Republic of Kyrgyzstan as well as Turkmenistan; and Peter Hancock as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Georgia concurrently accredited as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Azerbaijan.
